{"tid":1070971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咩方法追人還錢最有效￼","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T08:14:22.000Z","uid":232607,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5c832877e21182dc8d3aef94dae086c3dc15a8","tid":1070971,"uid":232607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"事緣我有一個朋友a 話熟唔熟 話唔熟又唔係 <br />\n而借錢嗰個係朋友a個朋友 (叫佢朋友b)<br />\n因為朋友b屋企人喺香港都叫有啲地位 同埋我見佢係朋友a個fd 所以就借左四萬蚊俾佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數數手指 佢已經差我就黎一年<br />\n我係無佢電話號碼嘅 同佢溝通都係靠ig direct message <br />\n依幾個月我仲有send訊息俾佢<br />\n由初初好似好有誠意咁話幾時會還 <br />\n到上個月睇完我message然後一個禮拜先覆我<br />\n今個月仲過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直情睇都冇睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我發現佢ig hide左我story 係咪驚比我知道佢周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有叫朋友a幫我問一問佢 始終佢哋熟啲 但係朋友a敷衍我 應該冇諗住幫我問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然四萬蚊話多唔多 但係對最近手緊嘅我真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無過來人醒兩招俾我 定嗰四萬蚊已經凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果我比料蘋果動有冇用 因為佢係啲有啲地位嘅人個仔"},{"pid":"880011d5d262566b404e090bb0e1f4af2e9b56db","tid":1070971,"uid":29689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"40k 都唔多？<br />\n巴打本身應該都幾疊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好追啦"},{"pid":"1ced98cf46698ceb6d3650073c607f2b0744f68d","tid":1070971,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"放上連登囉"},{"pid":"c4d9e27e90327303b7444a433f50344c8c1e53fb","tid":1070971,"uid":224168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"憑佢實力借返黎既4萬蚊點解要還？<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e5da833acb87b4bf466908374ab8a4fe319916","tid":1070971,"uid":232607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"880011d5d262566b404e090bb0e1f4af2e9b56db","tid":1070971,"uid":29689,"li